verbyn, Cornouailles, Angleterre, son père, Hugh Treverbyn, avait 28 ans et sa mère, Theosanna, avait 22 ans. Il a épousé Margery Bloyou en 1305, à Ingoldsby, Lincolnshire, Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils et 2 filles. Il est décédé en 1314, à Polruan, Cornouailles, Angleterre, à l’âge de 38 ans."},"de":{"1276–1314":"1276–1314","1281–1326":"1281–1326","1298–1336":"1298–1336","1305–1342":"1305–1342","1306–1360":"1306–1360","1248–Male":"1248–Verstorben","1254–1325":"1254–1325","1360":"1360","1281":"1281","1290":"1290","1305":"1305","1326":"1326","1314":"1314","1325":"1325","1248":"1248","1336":"1336","1276":"1276","1298":"1298","1254":"1254","1342":"1342","1306":"1306","Treverbyn, Cornwall, England":"Treverbyn, Cornwall, England","Ingoldsby, Lincolnshire, England":"Ingoldsby, Lincolnshire, England","Polruan, Cornwall, England":"Polruan, Cornwall, England","Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, England","Devon, England":"Devon, England","lifeSummary":"Als Walter de Treverbyn 1276 in Treverbyn, Cornwall, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater Hugh Treverbyn 28 und seine Mutter Theosanna 22. Er hat 1305 in Ingoldsby, Lincolnshire, England Margery Bloyou geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn und 2 Töchter. Er starb 1314 im Alter von 38 Jahren in Polruan, Cornwall, England."},"ht":{"1276–1314":"1276–1314","1281–1326":"1281–1326","1298–1336":"1298–1336","1305–1342":"1305–1342","1306–1360":"1306–1360","1248–Male":"1248–Desede","1254–1325":"1254–1325","1360":"1360","1281":"1281","1290":"1290","1305":"1305","1326":"1326","1314":"1314","1325":"1325","1248":"1248","1336":"1336","1276":"1276","1298":"1298","1254":"1254","1342":"1342","1306":"1306","Treverbyn, Cornwall, England":"Treverbyn, Cornwall, England","Ingoldsby, Lincolnshire, England":"Ingoldsby, Lincolnshire, England","Polruan, Cornwall, England":"Polruan, Cornwall, England","Cornwall, England":"Cornwall, England","Devon, England":"Devon, England"},"hu":{"1276–1314":"1276–1314","1281–1326":"1281–1326","1298–1336":"1298–1